# State machine template — states + labelled transitions.
right
Idle: circle "Idle" fit
arrow "request" above
Loading: circle "Loading" fit
arrow "ok" above
Ready: circle "Ready" fit
arrow "close" above
Done: circle "Done" fit

# Error transition from Loading
arrow from Loading.s down 0.5 then right then up to Done.s "error" below
arrow from Ready.s down 0.4 then left to Idle.s "reset" below
